============================================================
Why |О”ОұвӮҒ|=5 skips at n=5
============================================================

At n=5:
  max|О”tвӮғ| = 3 (3 triples contain the flipped arc)
  max|О”dвӮ…| = 3 (1 five-element set, at most 3 directed 5-cycles change)
  max|О”ОұвӮҒ| = 6

  |О”ОұвӮҒ| = 5 requires |О”tвӮғ| + |О”dвӮ…| = 5 with SAME SIGN
  Possibilities: (3,2), (2,3)

  But from the joint distribution (computed in delta_h_gap.py):
    Only (О”tвӮғ, О”dвӮ…) pairs where signs match give high |О”ОұвӮҒ|:
    (-3,-3)вҶ’6, (-3,-1)вҶ’4, (-2,-2)вҶ’4, (-1,-2)вҶ’3, (1,2)вҶ’3, (2,2)вҶ’4, (3,1)вҶ’4, (3,3)вҶ’6

  Missing: (3,2) or (2,3) or (-3,-2) or (-2,-3)

  WHY? Because О”tвӮғ=3 (all 3 triples gain a cycle) constrains the
  tournament structure so strongly that О”dвӮ… can only be 1 or 3, not 2.

  Similarly, О”dвӮ…=3 means the 5-cycle gains 3 directed cycles,
  which constrains О”tвӮғ to be exactly 3 (forced by the same structure).

  The (3,2) and (2,3) combinations require conflicting structural constraints.

============================================================
At n=6: gaps at |О”ОұвӮҒ| = 14, 15
============================================================

At n=6:
  max|О”tвӮғ| = 4
  max|О”dвӮ…| = 12 (4 five-sets Г— 3 max change each)
  max|О”ОұвӮҒ| = 16

  |О”H/2| takes values {0,1,...,13,16} вҖ” skipping 14, 15.

  |О”ОұвӮҒ| = 14 would need (4,10) or (3,11) or (2,12) вҖ” extreme near-max 5-cycle changes
  |О”ОұвӮҒ| = 15 would need (3,12) or (4,11)
  |О”ОұвӮҒ| = 16 achieved: needs (4,12) вҖ” ALL triples and ALL five-sets max out

  So the gap is at |О”ОұвӮҒ| = max - 1 and max - 2.
  At n=5: gap at |О”ОұвӮҒ| = max - 1 (= 5)
  At n=6: gaps at |О”ОұвӮҒ| = max - 2 and max - 1 (= 14, 15)

  This suggests: the EXTREME simultaneous change can happen (max),
  but slightly-less-than-max requires contradictory constraints.

Prediction for n=7:
  max|О”tвӮғ| = 5
  max|О”dвӮ…| вүӨ 30
  max|О”ОұвӮҒ| вүӨ 35
  Expected gaps near 34 and 33

Note: 7-cycles add more, so actual max |О”ОұвӮҒ| is higher.
The gap pattern should still appear near the max.
